        <p class="text-xl text-primary leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Board advisory, executive coaching, and strategic consulting—specialized guidance that draws on both deep experience and evidence-based methodology.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary leading-relaxed">
          17 years at board level across NHS, technology, financial services, and professional services. IoD Ambassador, FRSPH Fellow, FCMI Fellow—support for 100+ organizations navigating complex challenges.
        </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Conference Image -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <img
            src="/images/iod-conference-83.jpg"
            alt="Craig Fearn at IoD Conference"
            class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
            width="800"
            height="600"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
